# Classic CSE Dept REU Proposal
- [Application Form](https://forms.office.com/r/RzaKTe3zuZ)

### Requirements
- Undergrad recruitment blurb (1-2 paragraphs), if you have not identified a candidate
- Proposal (2 page max) - see [Template](https://ur2phd-program-uta.github.io/ur2phd-uta-call/template)
**Proposal deadline: January 19, 2026

The CSE Department will fund up to **20 students across the CSE REU and UR2PhD Program**  
> **Note:** If undergraduates are not identified at submission, we will issue a call to CSE undergrads, gather applications, and allow you to select students.

# Benefits
Undergraduates who complete the course will receive a **$500 scholarship**, disbursed via myMav in Spring 2026.

Completion requirements:
- Submit a final deliverable package: poster PDF + 1-2 page summary + link to artifacts (repo, design files, dataset, etc.) by April 30
- Present at Innovation Day (April 14, 2026) or other conference 
